Maybe it's an inner sense of inadequacy that relentlessly drives you forward, inadequacy can be a terrible slave master.

22:05.506 --> 22:10.831
The sense that I always have to do more, prove more, be more, and that nothing I ever do will be enough.

22:13.654 --> 22:16.757
Maybe right alongside that, it's the master of shame.

22:18.138 --> 22:22.042
It's things that you've done in your past that have come to define you.

22:23.504 --> 22:25.746
Maybe relate to Lady Macbeth.

22:26.326 --> 22:28.308
Remember Lady Macbeth and Shakespeare's play?

22:29.490 --> 22:34.034
She at one point is sleepwalking in a dream state.

22:34.722 --> 22:38.326
And in her waking life, she had plotted some murders.

22:39.347 --> 22:42.230
And the guilt of what she has done continues to haunt her.

22:42.250 --> 22:46.375
And now in this dream state, she looks and she sees blood on her hands.

22:47.276 --> 22:50.640
And she begins frantically trying to scrub the blood off.

22:50.860 --> 22:53.383
And she can't make the blood go away.

22:53.463 --> 22:58.488
And frantically, she shouts out, out, out, damn spot.

23:00.050 --> 23:01.412
Who will make this go away?

23:02.232 --> 23:03.634
Why can't I escape

23:03.746 --> 23:05.228
the things of my past.

23:07.671 --> 23:15.301
And sometimes some of us have those spots, those things that stain our conscience that we can't get rid of.

23:15.361 --> 23:23.692
And they're the spots that we wonder, could God ever forgive someone like me who has done something like that?

23:26.375 --> 23:31.602
Maybe you don't feel enslaved to anything, but maybe wandering in the wilderness rings a bell.

23:32.738 --> 23:37.362
You're on the move, but you're not sure where to or why.

23:38.904 --> 23:40.105
What is the purpose of it all?

23:41.767 --> 23:43.828
Is there any purpose?

23:45.190 --> 23:47.192
Is there a reason for you to live?

23:49.093 --> 23:55.500
Is the purpose you're living for really the purpose that you were made for or is it just a self-imposed illusion?

23:58.102 --> 23:59.363
Well, here's the message of the gospel.

24:01.425 --> 24:02.386
There is a God.

24:03.298 --> 24:03.899
who loves you.

24:06.041 --> 24:08.624
A God who wants you to be free.

24:10.586 --> 24:14.770
A God who knows exactly what your purpose is because he is your creator.

24:16.352 --> 24:19.255
