25:08.209 --> 25:12.536
When he said to the Israelites in Egypt, go ahead, follow Moses across that sea.

25:12.596 --> 25:16.081
When he said to Joshua, go ahead, follow the priests across that river.

25:16.482 --> 25:27.539
There's a step of faith that says, I don't fully understand all of this, but I believe this is the way out and to take the step of faith to follow.

