29:29.301 --> 29:36.210
Stand your ground, putting on the belt of truth and the body armor of God's righteousness, for shoes put on the peace,

29:36.290 --> 29:39.754
that comes from the good news so that you will be fully prepared.

29:41.336 --> 29:45.802
