45:33.026 --> 45:34.268
Father again, we just give you thanks.

45:35.811 --> 45:41.059
We give you thanks that we are living in your story that is so much greater than our own.

45:43.423 --> 45:47.771
Help us, I pray, to fight, to fight that you given to each one of us.

45:49.253 --> 45:56.946
And we look forward to the day that we celebrate the end of all conflict with you when your kingdom comes.

